          </div>
          <div class="doc-link-arrow">→</div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="ds-body rv" style="margin-top:28px">
        To request any of the above documents, contact RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC at <strong>(646) 403-3807</strong> or email <strong>invest@radianx.io</strong>. Documents will be provided promptly and at no charge. Clients are entitled to request updated copies of the Form ADV at any time.
      </p>
